title: Checking filter using pairwise testing
description: This test case can be use many times for entering all values that listed in Parvise Filter sort.xlsx file.
steps_actions:
1. Select value at accordeon "Категория" that indicated at file "Parvise Filter sort.xlsx" at the "Категория" column.
2. Select value at accordeon "Бренды" that indicated at file "Parvise Filter sort.xlsx" at the "Бренды" column.
3. Select value at accordeon "Цена" that indicated at file "Parvise Filter sort.xlsx" at the "Цена" column.
4. Click "Фильтр" button.
steps_result:
1. Checkbox of "Категория" parametr from parametrs liist is chosed.
2. Checkbox of "Бренды" parametr from parametrs liist is chosed.
3. Checkbox of "Цена" parametr from parametrs liist is chosed.
4. Page with items that corresponds our parametrs is opened.If no such items exist, the page displays a notification: "Товаров, соответствующих вашему запросу, не обнаружено."

title: Adding random item and creating the order.
description: Critical path of user from entering site to creating order.
steps_actions:
1. Click at random item in the list of items with status "В наличии". For example at "БРЕДБЕРРИ Комод с ящиками".
2. Click at the button "В корзину"
3. Click at button "Оформление заказа" at popup window.
4. Input name in the "Имя" field.
5. Input surname in the "Фамилия" field.
6. Select country from "Страна/регион" select field.
7. Input home number and street in "Номер дома и название улицы" field.
8. Input city in the "Населённый пункт" field.
9. Select region from "Область / район" select field.
10. Input Index in "Почтовый индекc" field
11. Input phone number in "Телефон" field
12. Input email in field "Email".
13. Click at the "Подтвердить заказ" button
steps_result:
1. Page with chosed item is opened.
2. Item is added to the basket. Appeared popup basket window from the right side.
3. Page
https://test.qa.studio/?page_id=10
is opened.
4. The system allows you to enter text.
5. The system allows you to enter text.
6. Country "Россия" is selected.
7. The system allows you to enter text.
8. The system allows you to enter text.
9. Region "Московская область" is selected
10. The system allows you to enter text.
11. The system allows you to enter text.
12. The system allows you to enter text.
13. Order created. Page 
https://test.qa.studio/?page_id=10&order-received=11765&key=wc_order_cpzAk9kyPnVZF
is opened.
